The <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Acid Rain</ENAMEX> Program is achieving its emission reduction goal
at a fraction of the estimated costs because it allows and
encourages innovative thinking and long range planning<TIMEX TYPE="TIME">.1</TIMEX> The
existing program establishes a cap on <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">SO2</ENAMEX> emissions to ensure that
