Business as Usual 

The <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">President</ENAMEX>'s flexible, market-based approach to reducing
emissions from power generators stands in sharp contrast to the
complex web of existing regulations which currently confront the
industry. Over <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the years</TIMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Congress</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">EPA</ENAMEX> and the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">States</ENAMEX> have
