<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">technologies</ENAMEX> for the control of <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">SO2</TIMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NOx</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">mercury</ENAMEX> emissions
